{"id":35581,"date":"2020-08-30T09:16:16","date_gmt":"2020-08-30T08:16:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?p=35581"},"modified":"2021-10-25T09:20:34","modified_gmt":"2021-10-25T08:20:34","slug":"dambulla","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/dambulla\/","title":{"rendered":"6 Best Things To Do in Dambulla"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">6 Things To Do in Dambulla<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dambulla is not the best place to stay in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"undefined (opens in a new tab)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>, but it definitely has a lot of interesting things to offer. Spend one or two nights here a do trips to the following sights.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114136\/Pidurangala-Rock-sri-lanka.jpg\" alt=\"Pidurangala Rock sri lanka\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"Pidurangala Rock sri lanka\" class=\"wp-image-34181 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114136\/Pidurangala-Rock-sri-lanka.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114136\/Pidurangala-Rock-sri-lanka-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114136\/Pidurangala-Rock-sri-lanka-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114136\/Pidurangala-Rock-sri-lanka-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114136\/Pidurangala-Rock-sri-lanka-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/202