 (opens in a new tab)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">UNESCO World Heritage site<\/a> since the climb to the top is challenging! The Lion Rock is a 30-minute drive from Dambulla. Travelers often choose to spend the night in Dambulla because the accommodation is much more affordable.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/sigiriya-lion-rock\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sigiriya Lion Rock, Everything you need to know<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114122\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-archeology-2-590x810.jpg\" alt=\"sigiriya lion rock sri lanka archeology\"><\/noscript><img width=\"246\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sigiriya lion rock sri lanka archeology\" data-id=\"34197\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114122\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-archeology-2.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/travel-blog\/pidurangala-rock-sigiriya\/attachment\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-archeology-2\/\" class=\"wp-image-34197 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114122\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-arc